# Append-only logs: auto-resolve "both branches appended at EOF" by keeping
# both sides instead of raising a conflict. Parallel agents on different issues
# each add an issue-keyed entry at the end (see docs/DECISIONS.md header); the
# `union` driver concatenates them on merge/rebase rather than stopping for a
# hand-resolution that is always "keep both". Relies on the append-only rule —
# union is blind to edits of existing lines, so never rewrite a settled entry on
# a feature branch.
docs/DECISIONS.md merge=union
